          "reviewBody": "Very bad school in all aspects.\n1)They say school has ampetheatre, I say it  is a hot chamber as all  outdoor of the air conditioner(principal room,  Headmistress\nroom) are fitted there emitting hot air which is not good for any ones health.\n2) The teachers are dirty  poltics minded, they Target n take revenge from students. The teachers who r not capable to control the class target some students n give them mental pressure  n parents too.\n3)The School conducts annual day program in which only the students who r selected r invited  for which they are  charged   certain money . The other students who are not selected are not  allowed to see the program  n give them off day.\n4)The teacher give class work which are not  checked chapter wise but only after 2months or 3months thus not reviewing properly.\nVery ill managed School.\nThink twice before getting admission of ur child there.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
