          "reviewBody": "DPS Howrah is one of the renowned school in Howrah, couple of areas which I really felt make this School best is class\n1) Experienced and Skilled teachers\n2) Focus on extra curricular activities - Which is really important now a days\n3) Very structured method of teaching\n\nEBI\n1) Management should focus in discipline part, as along with education, discipline is important to become successful in life",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
