          "reviewBody": "As a parent I am having lots of wonderful and satisfying experience every day, being connected with this school. The dedication of the Faculty along with DPSH team contributes to the excellent guidance towards each student throughout the session. Not only academic curriculum, various other activities for the students always needs special mention. Involvement of the students in so many special activities plays a vital role in their proper development. Thank you all for your constant guidance.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
